c: 3
v: 119
t: "Here you are! You have love (and fondness) for them, but they do not love you at all, (even though) you believe in all the scriptures. When they see you, they say, \"We believe!\" But when they are alone, they bite off their fingertips in their rage towards you. Say, \"Die (and fade away) in your fury! Allah is well Aware of that which is in your heart"